<lb n="7" break="no"/>jāsatisaṁvatsarada kārttika damāvāśye Ā<note n="239-1">The letter ka is written below the line.</note>
<lb n="8" break="no"/>dityavāra saṁkramāṇanimittadiṁ svasti ya
<lb n="9" break="no"/>maniyamasvādhyāyadhyānadhāraṇamō
<lb n="10" break="no"/>nānuṣṭhānajapasamādhiśīlagu
