<lb n="13" break="no"/>disaṁsiddha sarbbanamaśyaduttamadagrahā
<lb n="14" break="no"/>raṁ saṁtheya kō<unclear>rā</unclear>vūradaśēṣamahā
<lb n="15" break="no"/>janaṁgaḷige yalliya mūliga bammara
